Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/sychen/vimrc.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Plugin Management (using vim-plug)

* Edit

    vim ~/.vim/plugin-list.vim

* Operations (vim-plug)

    :PlugInstall
    :PlugUpdate
    :PlugUpgrade

=======================================================
Assistant Windows
=======================================================

 <F3>     <F4>       <F5>
Tagbar             NerdTree
      Grep&Quickfix

